                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Machines now. A TM holds eight teachings before the coils burn out, and no, I do not repair them — League ordinance, not stinginess. Eight lessons from one disc. Spend them on a Pokemon you intend to keep."
                        }
                    ],
