                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Three badges. The glass opens. These are the machines that decide matches — setup, coverage, the moves a leader would rather you did not carry into the rematch. Same eight-use burn, same no-repair. Choose like it is the last disc in the falls, because on a bad week it is."
                        }
                    ],
